    <strong>Old Wallet detected:</strong> We see you are using an old wallet. Please transfer your funds to a newly
    created wallet as soon as possible. Support for 'old' wallets will be discontinued <b>July 15, 2014</b>.
    <a href="https://forums.counterparty.co/index.php?topic=321.0" target="_blank">More info</a>.
</div>

{{ if (xcp_store_url) { }}
